MNI Datasets

mni_datasets.Rd

MNI Datasets

mni_datasets(type = c("nifti", "minc1", "minc2"))

Arguments

type

Type of imaging, either MINC or NIfTI types

Value

A data.frame with names and groups

Examples

mni_datasets()
